***
The code in this directory is very old and might not work properly
in modern platforms. We welcome patches to bring it up to date.
***

PLRHO is a utility program to plot the electron density and other functions.
It was written as a complement to the SIESTA electronic-structure program,
by Jose M. Soler in December 1997.

Read plrho_guide.txt for user instructions.
Copyright by Jose M. Soler, 1997.



